= Fighting off litigators =
->
[ [[FfiiprojPriorEn| priorities]]
]
----

''FFII is being attacked by people who are trying to consume our ressources with legal costs.  We need to find ways to reduce these costs.''

 * nutzwerk: warn all parties who could receive lawyer threat letters, establish channels for emergency cases
 * nutzwerk (phm & lawyers): deal with [[http://nutzwerk.ffii.org|Nutzwerk]]: documents needed to make IT-unsavvy courts understand what is wrong with Nutzwerk.  Will be made accessible at http://nutzwerk.ffii.org/ffii/
